-women-rights-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIshwar%20Chandra%20Vidyasagar%2C%20a%20reformer%20from%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20refused%20to%20accept%20this%20cruelty%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctradition.%E2%80%9D%20He%20lobbied%20the%20British%2C%20rallied%20public%20opinion%2C%20and%20eventually%20succeeded.%20The%201856%20law%20legally%20allowed%20Hindu%20widows%20to%20remarry%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20was%20almost%20unthinkable%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20marriage.%20It%20was%20about%20giving%20women%20a%20second%20chance%20at%20life.%20A%20radical%20concept%20back%20then%20%E2%80%94%20still%20powerful%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20The%20Married%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Property%20Act%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%3A%201874%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%3A%20British%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20thing%3A%20before%20this%20law%2C%20once%20a%20woman%20got%20married%2C%20anything%20she%20owned%20%E2%80%94%20money%2C%20land%2C%20jewellery%2C%20automatically%20belonged%20to%20her%20husband.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sell%20it%2C%20invest%20it%2C%20or%20use%20it%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Act%20changed%20that.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F185674%2Findia-women-rights-property-inheritance-law-buying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt%20legally%20recognised%20a%20married%20woman%E2%80%99s%20right%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20hold%20property%20in%20her%20own%20name.%20She%20could%20now%20have%20legal%20ownership%20over%20her%20earnings%20and%20belongings%2C%20even%20while%20being%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20early%20attempt%20to%20say%3A%20a%20woman%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20extension%20of%20her%20husband.%20She%20has%20a%20legal%20identity.%20She%20can%20earn%2C%20own%2C%20and%20control.%20A%20quietly%20radical%20move%20for%20a%20society%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20think%20women%20needed%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20The%20Child%20Marriage%20Restraint%20Act%20(Sarda%20Act)%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%3A%201929%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%3A%20All%20of%20British%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChild%20marriage%20was%20not%20just%20common%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20the%20norm.%20Girls%20were%20married%20off%20before%20they%20even%20hit%20puberty.%20The%20Sarda%20Act%2C%20named%20after%20judge%20and%20reformer%20Harbilas%20Sarda%2C%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20real%20attempt%20to%20put%20an%20age%20limit%20on%20this%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Child%20marriage%20was%20abolished%20by%20a%20law%20that%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-461638%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChild%20marriage%20was%20abolished%20by%20a%20law%20that%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%20Picture%20source%3A%20garystockbridge%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20it%20illegal%20for%20girls%20under%2014%20and%20boys%20under%2018%20to%20marry%20(later%20raised%20to%2018%20and%2021).%20Of%20course%2C%20implementation%20was%20patchy.%20But%20the%20message%20was%20clear%3A%20girls%20were%20not%20commodities%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20like%20dowry%20items.%20They%20deserved%20a%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20law%20planted%20the%20seed%20for%20future%20reforms%20and%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20government%20stepping%20into%20personal%2C%20cultural%20territory%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20then%2C%20and%20still%20isn%E2%80%99t%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20The%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%3A%201956%2C%20Amended%202005%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%3A%20Post-independence%20India%20for%20Hindus%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20%26amp%3B%20Sikhs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20any%20woman%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9880s%20or%20%E2%80%9890s%20about%20inheritance%2C%20and%20chances%20are%20she%E2%80%99ll%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20brother%20got%20everything.%E2%80%9D%20Before%201956%2C%20women%20in%20Hindu%20families%20were%20not%20legal%20heirs%20to%20joint%20family%20property.%20That%20meant%20land%2C%20ancestral%20homes%2C%20and%20farmland%20%E2%80%94%20all%20went%20to%20the%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201956%20law%20made%20daughters%20legal%20heirs%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20the%20right%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20equal%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20father%20was%20still%20alive.%20It%20was%20only%20with%20the%202005%20amendment%20that%20the%20law%20went%20further%2C%20declaring%20daughters%20as%20coparceners%20%E2%80%94%20equal%20in%20rights%20and%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20plain%20terms%3A%20if%20your%20brother%20gets%20land%2C%20you%20get%20land.%20No%20questions.%20No%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20The%20Dissolution%20of%20Muslim%20Marriages%20Act%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%3A%201939%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%3A%20British%20India%20(for%20Muslims)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20one%20is%20often%20overlooked%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20quietly%20one%20of%20the%20most%20empowering.%20It%20gave%20Muslim%20women%20the%20right%20to%20legally%20divorce%20their%20husbands%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20was%20historically%20much%20easier%20for%20men%20via%20talaq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20listed%20specific%20grounds%3A%20cruelty%2C%20impotence%2C%20desertion%2C%20non-payment%20of%20maintenance%2C%20and%20even%20failure%20to%20perform%20marital%20obligations.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20about%20ending%20marriage%20lightly%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20about%20giving%20women%20the%20legal%20tools%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20abuse%20or%20neglect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184639.678-1751548725.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20laws%20were%20able%20to%20carve%20a%20place%20for%20women%20in%20society%20-%20a%20respectable%20one.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184639.678-1751548725.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184639.678-1751548725-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184639.678-1751548725-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184639.678-1751548725-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184639.678-1751548725-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-461642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20laws%20were%20able%20to%20carve%20a%20place%20for%20women%20in%20society%20%E2%80%93%20a%20respectable%20one.%20Picture%20source%3A%20garystockbridge%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20time%20when%20divorce%20carried%20heavy%20stigma%2C%20this%20law%20handed%20Muslim%20women%20a%20voice%20in%20their%20own%20futures.%20A%20huge%20shift%2C%20especially%20considering%20how%20few%20global%20legal%20systems%20allowed%20this%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20laws%20didn%E2%80%99t%20magically%20fix%20everything.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20dismantle%20patriarchy%20overnight%20or%20make%20Indian%20society%20suddenly%20gender-equal.%20But%20they%20did%20something%20just%20as%20powerful%20%E2%80%94%20they%20carved%20space%20for%20women%20in%20a%20legal%20system%20that%20had%20long%20ignored%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20each%20time%20a%20girl%20goes%20to%20school%20instead%20of%20getting%20married%2C%20a%20woman%20owns%20land%20in%20her%20name%2C%20or%20a%20widow%20finds%20love%20again%20%E2%80%94%20we%E2%80%99re%20living%20the%20legacy%20of%20these%20forgotten%20feminist%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751617019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T181749.693-1751547795.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D461335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20widow%20remarriage%20to%20the%20right%20to%20property%20and%20divorce%20%E2%80%94%20these%20early%20Indian%20laws%20gave%20women%20power%20in%20a%20time%20when%20society%20barely%20gave%20them%20a%20voice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F461335%2Fearly-indian-feminist-laws%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Pocket-Sized%20Device%20Can%20Test%20Your%20Soil%20in%205%20Minutes%3B%20Here%E2%80%99s%20How%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%2C%20Indian%20farmers%20have%20relied%20on%20traditional%20wisdom%20and%20visual%20cues%20to%20care%20for%20their%20land.%20Decades%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324349%2Fmaharashtra-agriculture-entomologist-sangita-sawalakhe-vidarbha-biotech-biopesticides-biofertilisers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoveruse%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20left%20the%20soil%20exhausted%20and%20less%20productive.%20About%20fifty%20years%20ago%2C%20producing%20two%20tonnes%20of%20crops%20per%20hectare%20required%20just%2054%20kilograms%20of%20fertiliser.%20Today%2C%20that%20same%20yield%20demands%20over%20280%20kilograms%2C%20which%20is%20a%20startling%20sign%20that%20the%20soil%20is%20no%20longer%20responding%20the%20way%20it%20once%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFertilisers%20are%20added%20without%20knowing%20what%20the%20soil%20needs.%20And%20while%20soil%20testing%20could%20solve%20this%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20is%20slow%2C%20inconvenient%2C%20and%20often%20too%20expensive.%20Farmers%20must%20collect%20half%20a%20kilo%20of%20soil%2C%20send%20it%20to%20a%20distant%20lab%2C%20and%20then%20wait%2010%20to%2015%20days%2C%20by%20which%20time%20seeds%20have%20already%20been%20sown%2C%20and%20fertilisers%20have%20already%20been%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20significant%20breakthrough%20has%20finally%20provided%20a%20solution%20to%20this%20problem.%20Developed%20by%20Dr%20Rajul%20Patkar%2C%20co-founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318062%2Fiit-bombay-scientist-dr-rajul-patkar-innovates-portable-soil-testing-device-for-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProximal%20Soilsens%20Technologies%2C%20%E2%80%98NutriSens%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20being%20called%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20smallest%20soil%20testing%20system.%20This%20handheld%20device%20offers%20accurate%20and%20lab-like%20results%2C%20not%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20but%20in%20under%20five%20minutes.%20And%20all%20it%20takes%20is%20a%20few%20simple%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20how%20you%20can%20use%20NutriSens%20to%20test%20your%20soil%20quickly%20and%20easily%2C%20without%20any%20lab%20visits%2C%20delays%2C%20or%20guesswork%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NutriSens%20offers%20accurate%20and%20lab-like%20results%2C%20not%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20but%20in%20under%20five%20minutes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-03T184841.692_11zon-1751548738-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2F